Summary: Tourist in Trinidad Tobago claims to shoot video of ufo's
divs: Sighting DetailsI just received this by e-mail from a friend, in it tourists claimed that while vacationing in Stone Haven Bay, Trinidad Tobago, they decided to see the sun rise and film the scene, they just happened to catch these two ufo's. My personal opinion is that it's a hoax but it would be interesting to have some video specialist take a look at it just for the heck of it.
